{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782413963384,"sessionID":"ses_10050fa72ffe1d7GU3GCs1clsN","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_u8hlfUMOtBp4QtyM7mFiBI5s","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-std\\collection\\README.md","offset":1,"limit":220},"output":"<path>D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-std\\collection\\README.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # 仓颉语言集合数据结构 Skill\n2: \n3: ## 1. 概述\n4: \n5: `std.collection` 包提供丰富的泛型集合数据结构和函数式迭代操作，是仓颉标准库中最常用的包之一。\n6: \n7: **导入**：`import std.collection.*`\n8: \n9: ---\n10: \n11: ## 2. 集合类型\n12: \n13: ### 2.1 ArrayList — 动态数组\n14: \n15: 最常用的线性集合，基于数组实现，支持随机访问和动态扩容。\n16: \n17: | 方法 / 属性 | 说明 |\n18: |-------------|------|\n19: | `ArrayList<T>()` | 创建空列表 |\n20: | `ArrayList<T>(capacity: Int64)` | 指定初始容量 |\n21: | `ArrayList<T>(elements: Collection<T>)` | 从集合构造 |\n22: | `ArrayList<T>(size: Int64, initElement: (Int64) -> T)` | 指定大小和初始化函数 |\n23: | `add(element: T): Unit` | 尾部追加 |\n24: | `add(element: T, at!: Int64): Unit` | 指定位置插入 |\n25: | `get(index: Int64): T` | 按索引读取 |\n26: | `set(index: Int64, element: T): Unit` | 按索引设置 |\n27: | `remove(at!: Int64): T` | 删除指定位置元素 |\n28: | `size: Int64` | 当前元素数量 |\n29: | `isEmpty(): Bool` | 是否为空 |\n30: | `contains(element: T): Bool` | 是否包含（需 T <: Equatable） |\n31: | `operator[](index: Int64)` | 下标访问（读/写） |\n32: | `iterator(): Iterator<T>` | 获取迭代器 |\n33: \n34: ```cangjie\n35: package test_proj\n36: import std.collection.*\n37: \n38: main() {\n39:     let list = ArrayList<String>()\n40:     list.add(\"Alice\")\n41:     list.add(\"Bob\")\n42:     list.add(\"Charlie\")\n43: \n44:     // 下标访问\n45:     println(list[0])  // Alice\n46: \n47:     // 迭代\n48:     for (name in list) {\n49:         print(\"${name} \")\n50:     }\n51:     println(\"\")  // Alice Bob Charlie\n52: \n53:     // 插入和删除\n54:     list.add(\"Dave\", at: 1)   // 在索引1插入\n55:     list.remove(at: 2)        // 删除索引2的元素(Bob)\n56:     println(\"size: ${list.size}\")  // size: 3\n57: \n58:     // 从数组构造\n59:     let nums = ArrayList<Int64>([1, 2, 3, 4, 5])\n60:     println(nums[2])  // 3\n61: }\n62: ```\n63: \n64: ### 2.2 HashMap — 哈希映射\n65: \n66: 基于哈希表的键值映射，要求 `K <: Hashable & Equatable<K>`。\n67: \n68: | 方法 / 属性 | 说明 |\n69: |-------------|------|\n70: | `HashMap<K, V>()` | 创建空映射 |\n71: | `HashMap<K, V>(capacity: Int64)` | 指定初始容量 |\n72: | `HashMap<K, V>(elements: Array<(K, V)>)` | 从键值对数组构造 |\n73: | `add(key: K, value: V): ?V` | 添加或更新，返回旧值 |\n74: | `get(key: K): ?V` | 获取值，不存在返回 None |\n75: | `contains(key: K): Bool` | 判断键是否存在 |\n76: | `remove(key: K): ?V` | 删除键值对，返回旧值 |\n77: | `size: Int64` | 当前元素数量 |\n78: | `operator[](key: K)` | 下标访问（读/写） |\n79: \n80: ```cangjie\n81: package test_proj\n82: import std.collection.*\n83: \n84: main() {\n85:     let map = HashMap<String, Int64>()\n86:     map[\"Alice\"] = 90\n87:     map[\"Bob\"] = 85\n88:     map[\"Charlie\"] = 95\n89: \n90:     // 读取\n91:     println(map[\"Alice\"])  // 90\n92: \n93:     // 安全读取\n94:     match (map.get(\"Dave\")) {\n95:         case Some(score) => println(\"Dave: ${score}\")\n96:         case None => println(\"Dave not found\")\n97:     }\n98: \n99:     // 遍历\n100:     for ((name, score) in map) {\n101:         print(\"${name}=${score} \")\n102:     }\n103:     println(\"\")\n104: \n105:     // 从数组构造\n106:     let m2 = HashMap<String, Int64>([(\"x\", 1), (\"y\", 2)])\n107:     println(\"contains x: ${m2.contains(\"x\")}\")  // true\n108: }\n109: ```\n110: \n111: ### 2.3 HashSet — 哈希集合\n112: \n113: 基于哈希表的集合，要求 `T <: Hashable & Equatable<T>`，元素不重复。\n114: \n115: ```cangjie\n116: package test_proj\n117: import std.collection.*\n118: \n119: main() {\n120:     let set = HashSet<Int64>()\n121:     set.add(1)\n122:     set.add(2)\n123:     set.add(3)\n124:     set.add(2)  // 重复元素不会添加\n125: \n126:     println(\"size: ${set.size}\")  // size: 3\n127:     println(\"contains 2: ${set.contains(2)}\")  // true\n128: \n129:     // 集合运算\n130:     let setA = HashSet<Int64>([1, 2, 3])\n131:     let setB = HashSet<Int64>([2, 3, 4])\n132:     // 遍历\n133:     for (v in setA) {\n134:         print(\"${v} \")\n135:     }\n136:     println(\"\")\n137: }\n138: ```\n139: \n140: ### 2.4 TreeMap — 有序映射\n141: \n142: 基于红黑树的有序映射，要求 `K <: Comparable<K>`，按键有序。\n143: \n144: ```cangjie\n145: package test_proj\n146: import std.collection.*\n147: \n148: main() {\n149:     let tm = TreeMap<String, Int64>([(\"banana\", 2), (\"apple\", 1), (\"cherry\", 3)])\n150: \n151:     // 按键有序遍历\n152:     for ((k, v) in tm) {\n153:         println(\"${k}: ${v}\")\n154:     }\n155:     // 输出: apple: 1, banana: 2, cherry: 3\n156: \n157:     println(\"size: ${tm.size}\")\n158: }\n159: ```\n160: \n161: ### 2.5 TreeSet — 有序集合\n162: \n163: 基于红黑树的有序集合，要求 `T <: Comparable<T>`，元素有序不重复。\n164: \n165: ```cangjie\n166: package test_proj\n167: import std.collection.*\n168: \n169: main() {\n170:     let ts = TreeSet<Int64>([3, 1, 4, 1, 5, 9, 2, 6])\n171: \n172:     // 有序且去重\n173:     for (v in ts) {\n174:         print(\"${v} \")\n175:     }\n176:     println(\"\")  // 1 2 3 4 5 6 9\n177: \n178:     println(\"size: ${ts.size}\")  // 7\n179: }\n180: ```\n181: \n182: ### 2.6 LinkedList — 双向链表\n183: \n184: 双向链表，支持高效的头尾插入删除。核心方法是 `addFirst`/`addLast`/`removeFirst`/`removeLast`，以及基于 `LinkedListNode` 的精确位置操作。\n185: \n186: `addFirst`/`addLast`/`addBefore`/`addAfter` 返回 `LinkedListNode<T>`，可用于后续精确位置插入或删除：\n187: \n188: ```cangjie\n189: package test_proj\n190: import std.collection.*\n191: \n192: main() {\n193:     let ll = LinkedList<String>()\n194:     let nodeA = ll.addLast(\"A\")\n195:     ll.addLast(\"B\")\n196:     ll.addLast(\"C\")\n197: \n198:     // 基于节点的精确位置插入\n199:     ll.addAfter(nodeA, \"X\")    // A 之后插入 X\n200:     for (v in ll) { print(\"${v} \") }\n201:     println(\"\")  // A X B C\n202: \n203:     // 基于节点删除\n204:     ll.remove(nodeA)\n205:     for (v in ll) { print(\"${v} \") }\n206:     println(\"\")  // X B C\n207: \n208:     println(\"size: ${ll.size}\")  // 3\n209: }\n210: ```\n211: \n212: ### 2.7 ArrayDeque / ArrayQueue / ArrayStack\n213: \n214: | 类型 | 接口 | 核心操作 |\n215: |------|------|----------|\n216: | `ArrayDeque<T>` | `Deque<T>` | `addFirst(T)`, `addLast(T)`, `removeFirst(): ?T`, `removeLast(): ?T`, `first: ?T`, `last: ?T` |\n217: | `ArrayQueue<T>` | `Queue<T>` | `add(T)`, `remove(): ?T`, `peek(): ?T` |\n218: | `ArrayStack<T>` | `Stack<T>` | `add(T)`, `remove(): ?T`, `peek(): ?T` |\n219: \n220: ```cangjie\n\n(Showing lines 1-220 of 386. Use offset=221 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# 仓颉语言集合数据结构 Skill\n\n## 1. 概述\n\n`std.collection` 包提供丰富的泛型集合数据结构和函数式迭代操作，是仓颉标准库中最常用的包之一。\n\n**导入**：`import std.collection.*`\n\n---\n\n## 2. 集合类型\n\n### 2.1 ArrayList — 动态数组\n\n最常用的线性集合，基于数组实现，支持随机访问和动态扩容。\n\n| 方法 / 属性 | 说明 |\n|-------------|------|\n| `ArrayList<T>()` | 创建空列表 |\n| `ArrayList<T>(capacity: Int64)` | 指定初始容量 |","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":".agents\\skills\\cangjie-std\\collection\\README.md","time":{"start":1782413963373,"end":1782413963384}},"id":"prt_f0026b042001BWRUeteaXgaFLG","sessionID":"ses_10050fa72ffe1d7GU3GCs1clsN","messageID":"msg_f00268f7d001hvv5aLbTbqMzIg"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782413963511,"sessionID":"ses_10050fa72ffe1d7GU3GCs1clsN","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_1f7oj5qlUCSV3sz0nPhttKfR","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-std\\random\\README.md","offset":1,"limit":220},"output":"<path>D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-std\\random\\README.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # 仓颉语言随机数 Skill\n2: \n3: ## 1. Random 类\n4: \n5: - 来自 `std.random.*`\n6: - 构造：`Random()` 使用默认种子，`Random(seed: UInt64)` 指定种子\n7: - `seed` 属性：获取当前种子值\n8: \n9: ---\n10: \n11: ## 2. 常用方法\n12: \n13: | 方法 | 说明 |\n14: |------|------|\n15: | `nextBool(): Bool` | 随机布尔值 |\n16: | `nextInt8/16/32/64(): IntN` | 随机有符号整数 |\n17: | `nextUInt8/16/32/64(): UIntN` | 随机无符号整数 |\n18: | `nextFloat16/32/64(): FloatN` | 随机浮点数，范围 [0.0, 1.0) |\n19: | `nextInt64(upper: Int64): Int64` | 随机整数，范围 [0, upper) |\n20: | `nextBytes(length: Int32): Array<Byte>` | 随机字节数组 |\n21: | `nextGaussianFloat64(mean!: Float64, sigma!: Float64): Float64` | 高斯分布随机数 |\n22: \n23: ```cangjie\n24: package test_proj\n25: import std.random.*\n26: \n27: main() {\n28:     let m: Random = Random(3)\n29:     let b: Bool = m.nextBool()\n30:     let c: Int8 = m.nextInt8()\n31:     print(\"b=${b is Bool},\")\n32:     println(\"c=${c is Int8}\")\n33:     return 0\n34: }\n35: ```\n36: \n37: ```cangjie\n38: package test_proj\n39: import std.random.*\n40: \n41: main(): Unit {\n42:     let rng = Random()\n43: \n44:     // 生成范围内的随机整数\n45:     let n = rng.nextInt64(100)\n46:     println(\"随机数 [0, 100): ${n}\")\n47: \n48:     // 生成随机浮点数\n49:     let f = rng.nextFloat64()\n50:     println(\"随机浮点 [0.0, 1.0): ${f}\")\n51: \n52:     // 生成随机字节数组\n53:     let bytes = rng.nextBytes(8)\n54:     println(\"随机字节长度: ${bytes.size}\")\n55: \n56:     // 高斯分布\n57:     let g = rng.nextGaussianFloat64(mean: 0.0, sigma: 1.0)\n58:     println(\"高斯随机数: ${g}\")\n59: }\n60: ```\n61: \n62: ---\n63: \n64: ## 3. 关键规则速查\n65: \n66: 1. `Random(seed)` 相同种子产生相同序列，适合可复现测试\n67: 2. `Random()` 使用系统默认种子，每次运行结果不同\n68: 3. `nextFloat16/32/64()` 返回 [0.0, 1.0) 左闭右开区间\n69: 4. `nextInt64(upper)` 参数必须大于 0，否则抛异常\n70: 5. `nextGaussianFloat64` 使用命名参数 `mean:` 和 `sigma:`\n71: 6. `Random` 非线程安全，多线程场景应各自创建实例\n\n(End of file - total 71 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# 仓颉语言随机数 Skill\n\n## 1. Random 类\n\n- 来自 `std.random.*`\n- 构造：`Random()` 使用默认种子，`Random(seed: UInt64)` 指定种子\n- `seed` 属性：获取当前种子值\n\n---\n\n## 2. 常用方法\n\n| 方法 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| `nextBool(): Bool` | 随机布尔值 |\n| `nextInt8/16/32/64(): IntN` | 随机有符号整数 |\n| `nextUInt8/16/32/64(): UIntN` | 随机无符号整数 |\n| `nextFloat16/32/64(): FloatN` | 随机浮点数，范围 [0.0, 1.0) |\n| `nextInt64(upper: Int64): Int64` | 随机整数，范围 [0, upper) |\n| `nextBytes(length: Int32): Array<Byte>` | 随机字节数组 |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".agents\\skills\\cangjie-std\\random\\README.md","time":{"start":1782413963501,"end":1782413963511}},"id":"prt_f0026b06e001Az9D7qom9Ghkws","sessionID":"ses_10050fa72ffe1d7GU3GCs1clsN","messageID":"msg_f00268f7d001hvv5aLbTbqMzIg"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782413963541,"sessionID":"ses_10050fa72ffe1d7GU3GCs1clsN","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_Xaw0YCZS48eVlHXCaehtPusL","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-std\\unittest\\README.md","offset":1,"limit":220},"output":"<path>D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-std\\unittest\\README.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # 仓颉语言单元测试 Skill\n2: \n3: ## 1. 快速入门\n4: \n5: ### 1.1 编译与运行\n6: ```bash\n7: # 基于 cjc 使用（处理简单文件或包）\n8: cjc code.cj test.cj --test -o test_binary\n9: ./test_binary\n10: \n11: # 基于 cjpm 使用（标准项目）\n12: cjpm test\n13: cjpm test src src/koo   # 测试指定包\n14: ```\n15: \n16: ### 1.2 测试文件约定\n17: - 测试文件命名为 `xxx_test.cj`，与 `xxx.cj` 并列\n18: - 测试模式下 `unittest` 和 `unittest.testmacro` 自动导入，无需显式 import\n19: \n20: ---\n21: \n22: ## 2. 测试实体\n23: \n24: ### 2.1 测试函数\n25: ```cangjie\n26: @Test\n27: func addTest() {\n28:     @Expect(add(2, 3), 5)\n29: }\n30: ```\n31: - 顶层函数标记 `@Test`，包含单个测试用例\n32: \n33: ### 2.2 测试类\n34: ```cangjie\n35: @Test\n36: class AddTests {\n37:     @TestCase\n38:     func addPositive() { @Expect(add(2, 3), 5) }\n39: \n40:     @TestCase\n41:     func addZero() { @Expect(add(2, 0), 2) }\n42: }\n43: ```\n44: - 类标记 `@Test`，须有无参构造函数\n45: - 方法标记 `@TestCase`，每个方法为一个测试用例\n46: \n47: ---\n48: \n49: ## 3. 断言\n50: \n51: ### 3.1 断言宏列表\n52: | 宏 | 失败行为 | 说明 |\n53: |----|----------|------|\n54: | `@Assert(a, b)` | 快速失败：立即停止测试 | 相等性断言 |\n55: | `@Expect(a, b)` | 软失败：记录失败，继续执行 | 相等性断言 |\n56: | `@Assert(condition)` | 快速失败 | 布尔断言 |\n57: | `@Expect(condition)` | 软失败 | 布尔断言 |\n58: | `@AssertThrows[ExType](expr)` | 快速失败 | 期望抛出异常 |\n59: | `@ExpectThrows[ExType](expr)` | 软失败 | 期望抛出异常 |\n60: | `@Fail(\"msg\")` | 强制失败，停止测试 | 强制标记失败 |\n61: | `@FailExpect(\"msg\")` | 强制失败，继续执行 | 强制标记失败 |\n62: | `@PowerAssert(expr)` | 快速失败 | 详细中间值图示 |\n63: \n64: - **`@Assert(a, b)` / `@Expect(a, b)` 要求 `a` 的类型实现 `Equatable<B>`**（`B` 为 `b` 的类型）。若类型未实现 `Equatable`（如自定义枚举），须先通过 `@Derive[Equatable]` 或手动实现 `Equatable` 接口\n65: \n66: ### 3.2 近似相等（浮点数）\n67: ```cangjie\n68: @Expect(1.0, 1.001, delta: 0.001)\n69: ```\n70: - 类型须实现 `NearEquatable<CT, D>`，内置支持 Float16/32/64\n71: - 也支持 `RelativeDelta` 相对误差：\n72:   ```cangjie\n73:   @Expect(1.0 != 1.901, delta: RelativeDelta(absolute: 0.001, relative: 0.02))\n74:   ```\n75: - 若 `delta` 参数不可用（取决于框架版本），可使用布尔断言替代：\n76:   ```cangjie\n77:   import std.math.*\n78:   @Expect(abs(actual - expected) < 0.001)\n79:   ```\n80: \n81: ### 3.3 自定义断言\n82: ```cangjie\n83: @CustomAssertion\n84: public func checkNotNone<T>(ctx: AssertionCtx, value: ?T): T {\n85:     match (value) {\n86:         case Some(v) => v\n87:         case None => ctx.fail(\"Expected non-None\")\n88:     }\n89: }\n90: // 使用：@Assert[checkNotNone](myValue)\n91: ```\n92: \n93: ---\n94: \n95: ## 4. 测试生命周期（仅限测试类）\n96: \n97: | 宏 | 执行时机 |\n98: |----|----------|\n99: | `@BeforeAll` | 所有测试用例执行前，执行一次 |\n100: | `@BeforeEach` | 每个测试用例执行前 |\n101: | `@AfterEach` | 每个测试用例执行后 |\n102: | `@AfterAll` | 所有测试用例执行后，执行一次 |\n103: \n104: 执行顺序：`BeforeAll` → (`BeforeEach` → `TestCase` → `AfterEach`)* → `AfterAll`\n105: \n106: ---\n107: \n108: ## 5. 参数化测试\n109: \n110: ### 5.1 值驱动\n111: ```cangjie\n112: @Test[x in [1, 2, 3]]\n113: func squareTest(x: Int64) {\n114:     @Expect(square(x), x * x)\n115: }\n116: \n117: @Test[x in 0..10]\n118: func rangeTest(x: Int64) { ... }\n119: ```\n120: \n121: ### 5.2 随机参数\n122: ```cangjie\n123: @Test[x in random()]\n124: func randomTest(x: Int64) { ... }\n125: ```\n126: - 生成约 200 个随机值，偏向边界值\n127: \n128: ### 5.3 多参数（笛卡尔积）\n129: ```cangjie\n130: @Test[x in [1, 2], y in [\"a\", \"b\"]]\n131: func multiParamTest(x: Int64, y: String) { ... }\n132: ```\n133: \n134: ### 5.4 类型参数化\n135: ```cangjie\n136: @Types[T in <Int64, Float64, String>]\n137: @Test\n138: func genericTest<T>() { ... }\n139: ```\n140: \n141: ### 5.5 可复用策略\n142: ```cangjie\n143: @Strategy[param in source]\n144: func myStrategy(param: SomeType): ReturnType { ... }\n145: \n146: @Test[data in myStrategy]\n147: func strategyTest(data: ReturnType) { ... }\n148: ```\n149: \n150: ---\n151: \n152: ## 6. 基准测试\n153: \n154: ### 6.1 基本用法\n155: ```cangjie\n156: @Test\n157: class MyBench {\n158:     @Bench\n159:     func sortBenchmark() {\n160:         let arr = generateArray(10000)\n161:         arr.sort()\n162:     }\n163: \n164:     @Bench[size in [1000, 10000, 100000]]\n165:     func paramBench(size: Int64) {\n166:         let arr = generateArray(size)\n167:         arr.sort()\n168:     }\n169: }\n170: ```\n171: - 使用 `cjpm bench` 运行\n172: - 框架自动处理预热、GC 噪声、统计分析（中位数、均值、置信区间）\n173: \n174: ### 6.2 测量源\n175: ```cangjie\n176: @Measure[TimeNow(Nanos), CpuCycles()]\n177: @Bench\n178: func measuredBench() { ... }\n179: ```\n180: - 可用测量源：`TimeNow`、`CpuCycles`、`Perf`（Linux 性能计数器）\n181: \n182: ---\n183: \n184: ## 7. 动态测试\n185: \n186: ```cangjie\n187: @TestBuilder\n188: func dynamicTests(): TestSuite {\n189:     TestSuite.builder(\"DynTests\")\n190:         .add(UnitTestCase.create(\"case1\") { @Expect(1, 1) })\n191:         .add(UnitTestCase.create(\"case2\") { @Expect(2, 2) })\n192:         .build()\n193: }\n194: ```\n195: - 编程方式构建测试套件\n196: \n197: ---\n198: \n199: ## 8. 测试模板\n200: \n201: ```cangjie\n202: @TestTemplate\n203: abstract class BaseTests {\n204:     @BeforeEach\n205:     func setup() { ... }\n206: \n207:     @TestCase\n208:     func commonTest() { ... }\n209: }\n210: \n211: @Test\n212: class MyTests <: BaseTests {\n213:     @TestCase\n214:     func specificTest() { ... }\n215: }\n216: ```\n217: - 定义可复用的测试用例和生命周期方法\n218: - 生命周期顺序：基类 `@Before*` 先执行，派生类 `@After*` 先执行\n219: \n220: ---\n\n(Showing lines 1-220 of 435. Use offset=221 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# 仓颉语言单元测试 Skill\n\n## 1. 快速入门\n\n### 1.1 编译与运行\n```bash\n# 基于 cjc 使用（处理简单文件或包）\ncjc code.cj test.cj --test -o test_binary\n./test_binary\n\n# 基于 cjpm 使用（标准项目）\ncjpm test\ncjpm test src src/koo   # 测试指定包\n```\n\n### 1.2 测试文件约定\n- 测试文件命名为 `xxx_test.cj`，与 `xxx.cj` 并列\n- 测试模式下 `unittest` 和 `unittest.testmacro` 自动导入，无需显式 import\n\n---","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":".agents\\skills\\cangjie-std\\unittest\\README.md","time":{"start":1782413963533,"end":1782413963541}},"id":"prt_f0026b0ee0011CoZTZhsguion6","sessionID":"ses_10050fa72ffe1d7GU3GCs1clsN","messageID":"msg_f00268f7d001hvv5aLbTbqMzIg"}}
